title: Anticipation killing me
body: Haven't played in months got a new laptop and am downloading game again but its taking foreveeeeeeeeeerrr >:( just want to get back to the summoners rift and see how much has changed

replies.body:
Hope you enjoy your time back! 

Make sure to catch up on all the patch notes before playing ranked =P there have been some big changes to the jungle and jungle items.

The community is a lot more supportive now so you should be fine to just jump straight back into ranked.... Everyone will be happy to help you :P

(edit: plz don't hate me :D)
